      "content": "the problem is that \"resting\" feels impossible when i'm still stuck in this reality. i can't just sleep it off or take a vacation. there's still the debt, the expectations, the constant pressure to perform... it's all still there when i wake up. i feel like i'm just being forced to keep existing in a cycle that's already dead. i just want a way to actually be still. a real stillness. like, a way to just opt out of the struggle entirely.",
